{"tid":430908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞市長籲: 加泰主席別宣布獨立","createTime":"2017-10-10T08:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T08:31:24.000Z","uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1afc631982d591dfa1aa16a391f960ad5bee5831","tid":430908,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1358177-20171010.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1358177-20171010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9PM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=86206dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1358177-20171010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=38b76086\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1358177-20171010.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治區議會今日稍後開會，主席普伊格蒙特將發表演說。自治區首府巴塞羅那市長科洛，呼籲普伊格蒙特不要單方面宣布獨立，並促請首相拉霍伊不要直接干預自治區。她表示，雙方應停止一切會破壞對話與調停契機的舉動，避免令局勢升溫。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙在野社會黨黨魁桑切斯亦表示，支持馬德里中央政府，認為加泰羅尼亞若果獨立，將破壞社會和諧。<br />\n<br />\n再有大型企業計劃將總部搬離加泰羅尼亞，包括基建、電訊公司及地產發展商。"},{"pid":"81752557cf27d15c8dd5dcf728ffe4ac3001823c","tid":430908,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1358177-20171010.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1358177-20171010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9PM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=86206dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1358177-20171010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=38b76086\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1358177-20171010.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治區議會今日稍後開會，主席普伊格蒙特將發表演說。自治區首府巴塞羅那市長科洛，呼籲普伊格蒙特不要單方面宣布獨立，並促請首相拉霍伊不要直接干預自治區。她表示，雙方應停止一切會破壞對話與調停契機的舉動，避免令局勢升溫。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙在野社會黨黨魁桑切斯亦表示，支持馬德里中央政府，認為加泰羅尼亞若果獨立，將破壞社會和諧。<br />\n<br />\n再有大型企業計劃將總部搬離加泰羅尼亞，包括基建、電訊公司及地產發展商。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本西班牙都唔同你傾，球證都係西班牙嘅人，對話仲有咩意思。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n車臣化先係王道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/163123_bfd7af7eaaf8df806cf3aa92284f3a89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F163123_bfd7af7eaaf8df806cf3aa92284f3a89.jpg&h=30baca09&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}